      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-a" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Lipius quickly became best friends with Loffy after he suddenly appeared before us.<BR>They were like twins. They wanted to explore places they've never seen before, and there was nothing that could stop them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-b" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>But true freedom can only be obtained from… death… or madness.<BR>Lipius opened the forbidden door, and you can see what happened next.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-b" image="QW_95.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Still, it would be Lipius who has the best chance of knowing where Loffy is.<BR>Can you go back there and ask him about Loffy? Please?<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Try going to the Wailing Wall)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-1-a" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Still walking?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I'm sorry, you're blocking my way… Oh, you look familiar.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-1-b" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Walking is all you can do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I am walking because walking is all I can do.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-1-c" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why are you suddenly talking about this?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I always had doubts about my role as the guardian of the pledge. I thought I had finally found my telesia when the queen candidate <FONT color=#a82424>Vayella</FONT> died and the pledge I took with her was gone. But in that case, maybe I can choose my telesia, instead of just accepting it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-1-d" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How about answering my question first...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>If you feel something is your telesia, and that really is your telesia, then maybe you can choose your own telesia. And you would have fulfilled your telesia if you live for that. Whatever you believe in is your telesia… So I’m nt lost. I'm just living my telesia.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-2" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Erm… hello?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius stares at you quietly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-2-a" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>I see……. So Lipius must have gone insane too… Well, it would be funny if Lipius still kept his sanity when the rest of us are in this state.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
